videos.headline: Auburn takes lead on 5-yard run
videos.description: Auburn RB JaTarvious Whitlow takes it 5 yards for the game's first score.

videos.headline: Auburn blocks punt, recovers deep in Arkansas territory
videos.description: Auburn's Jordyn Peters blocks Arkansas' punt, leading to a touchdown on the next drive.

videos.headline: Auburn takes kickoff to the house with 96-yard return
videos.description: Auburn's Noah Igbinoghene takes a 96-yard kickoff return to the house, extending the lead to 24-3 over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Whitlow piles onto score with 2nd TD
videos.description: JaTarvious Whitlow scores his second touchdown of the night, padding Auburn's lead.
